I"K{<h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">Applications</h1>
<p>This page shows some of the applications of the collected riboswitches. We listed four kinds of applications, ‘Developing new antibacterials’, ‘Synthetic Biology’, ‘Building biosensors’ and ‘Gene therapy’ as shown in the following tables. The representatives of FMN riboswitch-specific antibacterial compounds are presented, as shown in the figure below.
<br /><br /></p>
